{"tid":1366861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單幾句話你知點解我地要Fact Check，亂鳩咁傳唔好怪無面比。","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:04:08.000Z","uid":36797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"792ec7f17a07f91ad5a0ae8dfa8232cae3957483","tid":1366861,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"1.資訊爆炸<br />\n原本已人心惶惶，再亂咁黎好多辛苦拎番黎既偏中間市民會寧願唔理。<br />\n2.唔好學對家。<br />\n幽默諷刺方法用對家手法放大該講法既無稽係另一回事，唔需要FC因為明顯係假。<br />\n3.怕狼來了<br />\n<br />\n[基本功] 教大家咩叫 FACT CHECK<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357480</a><br />\n<br />\n心急想有人理唔係藉口，睇左上面個POST，有教到唔同情況得到唔同資訊應該點講，開POST用咩TOPIC。<br />\n另外標題黨絕不辜惜，一定要斷絕依個風氣。<br />\n我地而家多左街外人入黎LIHKG，佢地未必明你係玩膠鳩UP定認真。"},{"pid":"07605930e66739168af3f631150ba80820d50a51","tid":1366861,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n麻煩大家有啲Po冇Fact Check唔好push啦<br />\n例如Yoho靜音火警鐘結果fake news<br />\n啲push就成為咗助長白色恐怖"},{"pid":"bbd7d65c074f1a24c64e6456f7574271fe3768d8","tid":1366861,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d2f3f84fd8d0ac6b482919725b993f4f0577e9","tid":1366861,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}